window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Former <i>Bake Off</i> host, passionate animal lover and comedian Sue Perkins, is our indispensable guide to the animal kingdom. Join her on a comical, insightful and, at times, shocking nature trail around the world.</p><p>In this mad-cap adventure, she introduces us to the amazing, surprising and hysterical truth about all creatures great and small. From the African lungfish to the kangaroo, get ready for an irreverent, funny and often furry journey of discovery.</p><p>This is an Audible Original Podcast. Free for members. You can download all 13 episodes to your Library now.</p>"; 
